   "source": [
    "Задание по 4й неделе курса Математика для анализа данных\n",
    "Центральная предельная теорема своими руками"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#Импортируем необходимые библиотеки\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import scipy.stats as sts\n",
    "import math\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "В качестве распределения была выбрана функция genlogistic"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 95,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Входным параметром для функции genlogistic является параметр с\n",
    "c = 0.18\n",
    "genlogistic_rv = sts.genlogistic(c)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Нарисуем график распределения\n",
    "x = np.linspace(-25,5,100)\n",
    "pdf = genlogistic_rv.pdf(x)\n",
    "plt.plot(x, pdf)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.ylabel('$f(x)$')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$x$');"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Получим выборку из 1000 значений\n",
    "sample = genlogistic_rv.rvs(1000)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 96,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Построим гистограмму и теоретическую плотность распределения на одном графике \n",
    "x = np.linspace(-25, 5, 1000)\n",
    "pdf = genlogistic_rv.pdf(x)\n",
    "plt.plot(x, pdf, label='theoretical pdf', alpha=0.5)\n",
    "plt.hist(sample, label = 'pdf hist', bins=20, normed=True)\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.ylabel('$f(x)$')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$x$');"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 97,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "mean =  -5.2930273344428835\n",
      "variance =  33.80673242254215\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Вычислим среднее и дисперсии для распредления\n",
    "mean, var = sts.genlogistic.stats(c, moments='mv')\n",
    "print 'mean = ', mean\n",
    "print 'variance = ', var"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 98,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x = np.linspace(-25,5,1000)\n",
    "sample_number = 1000\n",
    "mean, var = sts.genlogistic.stats(c, moments='mv')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Определим функцию построения гистрограммы\n",
    "##  n - значения выборки\n",
    "##  rv - генератор случайной величины\n",
    "##  bins - количество корзин для гистограммы\n",
    "def build_hist(n, rv, bins):\n",
    "    # формируем выборку из средних величин\n",
    "    sample = np.array([])\n",
    "    for i in range(sample_number):\n",
    "        n_sample = rv.rvs(n)\n",
    "        n_mean = sum(n_sample) / n\n",
    "        sample = np.append(sample, n_mean)\n",
    "    # строим по полученной выборке гистограмму\n",
    "    plt.hist(sample, bins = bins, normed=True)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # строим теоретическое нормальное распределение поверх гистограммы\n",
    "    norm = sts.norm(mean, math.sqrt(var / n)) \n",
    "    pdf_theory = norm.pdf(x) \n",
    "    plt.plot(x, pdf_theory, label = 'PDF')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.ylabel('fraction of samples')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('$x$')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 99,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# пример для n = 5\n",
    "build_hist(n = 5, rv = genlogistic_rv, bins = 12)"

  },
